     <div class="date"> 
      <h1>第四十六章 蛇灵（1）</h1> 
      <div class="info">
       <span>作者：三</span>
       <a href="/txt10928/" title="返回《我当道士那些年》介绍页" id="book10928">我当道士那些年</a> 本章字节数:4709498
       <script type="text/javascript">article_nav('10928','4035647');</script> 
       <a href="http://www.80txt.com/txtxz/10928.html" class="txt" id="down10928">我当道士那些年txt下载</a>
